- [x] Tests written or updated
- [x] Code implemented
- [x] API contracts updated, if needed
- [x] Database rules followed, if needed
- [x] Permissions tested, if needed
- [x] Audit events tested, if needed
- [x] Visual evidence saved, if frontend
